data.name: Are you sure you want to delete this user?
data.value: Er du sikker på, at du vil slette denne bruger?

data.name: This action is irreversible. You are about to permanently delete the following user and all their associated data:
data.value: Denne handling er irreversibel. Du er ved at slette følgende bruger og alle deres tilknyttede data permanent:

data.name: This user account is managed by an OpenID Connect (OIDC) provider. Deleting the user here will only remove their access and data from this application. The account will still exist on your OIDC provider and may reappear after the next sync or if the user logs in again. To permanently delete this user, you must remove them from your OIDC provider.
data.value: Denne brugerkonto administreres af en OpenID Connect (OIDC)-udbyder. Hvis du sletter brugeren her, fjernes kun deres adgang og data fra denne applikation. Kontoen vil stadig eksistere på din OIDC-udbyder og kan dukke op igen efter næste synkronisering, eller hvis brugeren logger ind igen. For at slette denne bruger permanent, skal du fjerne dem fra din OIDC-udbyder.
